Package: ADNIMetabo
Title: Prepare and process ADNI metabolomics data
Version: 0.99.0
Date: 2024-12-17
Authors@R: 
    person("Dany", "Mukesha", , "danymukesha@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0001-9514-751X"))
Description: Alzheimer's Disease Neuroimaging Initiative (ADNI) provides 
    a list of omics, among them there is metabolomics data. We collected 
    those data and curated them with a closer look, to help users
    explore and navigate easily through the ADNI metabolomics
    datasets. It is possible to access various datasets from ADNI, 
    including demographic, clinical, biomarker, imaging, and cognitive 
    composite data.
